productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Isabela has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks monochromatic.
one of my hobbies is sailing. and when i'm sailing this works great.
My chicken loves to play with it.
one of my hobbies is poetry. and when i'm writing poems this works great.
heard about this on melodic death metal radio, decided to give it a try.
